            <h3>WHAT IS NOBLE BREWER?</h3>
            <div class="body-copy">
              <p>Noble Brewer is a new kind of beer club. We're dedicated to celebrating the pioneers of the the craft beer movement - the homebrewer. We believe a great beer should be savored and appreciated with friends so we focus on creating a tasting experience centered around the origination of the recipe and the people who create them.</p>
