            <h3>OUR PROCESS</h3>
            <div class="body-copy">
              <p>Our process starts with the homebrewer. Our community submits their favorite award-winning homebrews. Then, we pair the recipe creator with a professional brewery to make their beer. Once bottled, we ship the beer and the story behind the featured homebrewer to our members who, in turn, provide feedback to the brewers. The end result is unique, one-of-a-kind craft beers that can't be found anywhere else.</p>
            </div>
